<br>
&quot;I and you all know that because Scynthia lies on Ancient Amazon Grounds, I do not need the blessings of Olympian Gods because of the ways that we follow. I myself am a Goddess of such order by your rites, and in equality of eachother, I ask a blessing from you on my marriage to the Avatar.&quot;<br>
<br>
